  <brief_title>Continuing Lamivudine vs Switching to Entecavir in Patients With Detectable HBV DNA</brief_title>
  <official_title>Randomized, Open-Labelled Study Evaluating the Antiviral Efficacy, Safety, and Tolerability of Continuing Lamivudine Therapy or Switching to Entecavir in Subjects With Chronic Hepatitis B With Detectable HBV DNA</official_title>
